scripts.name: Smartschool+
scripts.description: Change your name and customize Smartschool! Search for other students! Calculate the total score of your grades! Add quick shortcuts. Adds a customizable menu bar for Smartschool. Calculate the total score of your grades. Removes useless buttons and adds quick shortcuts. You can change your name and profile picture by typing the word "change" on your keyboard. You can find all existing users by typing the word "find" on your keyboard.

scripts.name: Auto-login Smartschool
scripts.description: Automatically fills in your Smartschool login data. Most secure version released.
